edu.metrostate.ics372.thatgroup.clinicaltrial.catalog

Class TrialManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.metrostate.ics372.thatgroup.clinicaltrial.catalog.TrialManager

  • public class TrialManager
extends java.lang.Object
    The TrialManager is responsible for returning a Singleton instance of a this class. When the TrialManager instance is instantiated, a new instance of ClinicalTrialCatalog is created, associated with this TrialManager and can accessed via the TrialManager.getTrialCatalog() method.
    Author:
    That Group
